Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:20.57,flashback,Miki,0000,0000,0000,,Drink with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:27.63,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,It all started with the idol \NFukumoto Miki-chan's commercial.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.52,0:00:33.11,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I fell in love with Miki-chan \Nand her outfit at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:35.60,flashback,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,S-So cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:38.56,flashback,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,So cute! So cute! So cute! \NSo cute! So cute! So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:42.68,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,So when I found a photo from when \Nmy mom went to this school,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:44.50,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.84,0:00:48.26,flashback,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,If that's where you want to go, that's fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:49.80,flashback,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,but it'll be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:51.32,flashback,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.59,0:00:55.92,flashback,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Also... if I make it into Roubai Academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.30,0:01:03.66,flashback,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to make a sailor uniform for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:09.59,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I always admired how my mother \Nlooked when she was working.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.43,0:01:14.88,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I only had eyes for that sailor uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.38,0:01:25.32,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,And that sailor uniform is the \Nreason I got into this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:33.22,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,The principal said I could \Nwear either uniform, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:41.27,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I chose the sailor uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:17.67,sign_3520_34_Episode_One__The,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(482,1)\pos(100,70)}Episode Two \NSee You Tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:21.28,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man! I talked for too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:24.79,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,They're all bored now! I just know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:28.73,main,Tamura,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi-san? Are you finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:32.99,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! My best feature is that \Nmy body is really flexible,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:35.51,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,and there's one thing I do that always \Nmakes my little sister laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:38.28,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to finish by showing it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:44.12,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:05.94,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,After her big sister tries \Nso hard to look awesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:07.69,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a ghost now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:09.19,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,This always...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:12.35,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:17.34,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Um... yeah... I'm done now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:19.47,main,Tamura,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:27.96,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,I understand you a lot \Nbetter now, Akebi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:31.20,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that last bit \Nwas funny, personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.55,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Kizaki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:34.46,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Only...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.21,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,I think everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:41.57,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,well... only saw up your skirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:45.59,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:51.41,main,Hitomi,0000,0000,0000,,Washio Hitomi. I plan to \Njoin the volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:52.19,main,Hitomi,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
