Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:11.27,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:29.04,flashback,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we have lunch now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:29.82,flashback,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:35.91,main,Tamura,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, move your desks together the way \NI've drawn on the board to form groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:37.99,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:44.81,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you look great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:48.58,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,So do you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:53.41,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.50,main,Riri,0000,0000,0000,,Thank ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.83,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,She thanked me in a Kansai accent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:01.59,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Seat number 13, Minakami Riri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:06.06,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Here you... go...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:11.53,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Seat number 14, Hiraiwa Hotaru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:13.67,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:20.56,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Careful you don't spill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:21.89,main,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:29.40,italics,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi-san, if you give everyone that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:28.25,top,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,And... there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:29.39,top,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.05,italics,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:39.16,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Sitting around our desks like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:42.46,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like we're a family!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:45.47,main,Tamura,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:47.02,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:11.95,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,That's gotta be rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.58,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, please feel free to use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.68,main,Tomono,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:25.05,main,Tomono,0000,0000,0000,,I left my glasses case in my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.35,0:07:26.95,main,Tomono,0000,0000,0000,,This is a huge help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:28.98,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:32.77,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:35.76,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I wipe my sweat \Nwith that handkerchief earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:40.79,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:44.63,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that handkerchief...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:47.57,main,Tomono,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I used the part that's dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:54.11,italics,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun just watching her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:58.57,main,Tomono,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the handkerchief, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:01.09,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi Komichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:03.59,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Kojou Tomono-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:07.89,main,Tomono,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. You actually \Nremembered my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:09.73,main,Tomono,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:13.31,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Seat number 6, Kojou Tomono-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.43,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,She's a really nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:24.19,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're pretty popular, \Nright, Akebi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:27.88,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Seat number 2, Usagihara Touko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:30.95,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been popular in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:34.91,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You're the only one in \Na pure white sailor uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:37.19,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,And you wear it so well, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:39.28,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You're like an idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:41.42,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I-Ido...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:46.36,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can call me that all you want, \Nbut I won't do anything for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:49.29,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Kao! She said I look like an idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:52.74,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, your face is just my type, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:55.39,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, no one's ever said that to me before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:00.23,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,But the blazer looks nice too, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:02.00,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to wear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:04.47,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It looks really mature!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:06.63,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna wear one someday, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:10.42,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then... want to try it on now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:11.00,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:14.52,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:17.07,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.00,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me yours, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:22.24,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow! Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:28.84,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:30.49,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:32.39,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,She was just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.39,0:09:33.03,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:38.83,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,If you take that off, won't you \Nbe in just your underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:40.07,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:42.95,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're the serious type, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:46.16,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,You're just such a smooth talker, \NI walked right into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:50.01,italics,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no, you're just super accident-prone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:52.95,italics,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,I need to make sure no creepy \Npests get hold of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:54.12,top,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Cackle, cackle, cackle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:00.70,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You didn't go to \Ncram school, Akebi-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.11,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,That's so unusual!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.11,0:10:03.91,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:08.01,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just that almost everyone \Ntrying to get into Roubai goes to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.53,0:10:09.95,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,For instance...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:11.28,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,That girl there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:15.20,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Tanigawa Kei. She always scored \Nthe highest on mock exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:17.30,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go wrong having her as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:20.41,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,And that's Tatsumori Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:22.24,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,She went to the same cram school as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:24.02,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,She's short-tempered and gets mad easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:27.41,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,She called me out for talking during \Nstudy periods so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:30.48,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that your own fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:34.19,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:37.48,italicstop,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, everyone! This is Mika, second-year, \Nwith the broadcasting club!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:37.45,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,You and those two girls you pointed \Nout are from Tokyo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:38.41,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.48,0:10:38.56,italicstop,Miku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:41.79,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Kizaki-san's also from Tokyo, \Nand Kojou-san is from Nagano.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:41.68,italicstop,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,To all the new first-years, \Ncongrats on getting in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.68,0:10:42.57,italicstop,Miku,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:43.99,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,How do you all come to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:48.33,italicstop,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,This program is being broadcast into every \Nclassroom from the broadcasting club's station!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:44.66,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:46.92,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You either move here or stay in the dorms!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:51.54,italicstop,Miku,0000,0000,0000,,The goal is to broadcast all over Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:51.24,main,Tomono,0000,0000,0000,,I'm staying at my grandma's—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:52.52,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Dorm life for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:54.49,italicstop,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's time for Roubai's hit chart!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:54.49,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Kizaki-san's my neighbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:56.75,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:58.95,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:59.04,italicstop,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we've got the perfect \Ncongratulatory song for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:00.08,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:00.59,italicstop,Miku,0000,0000,0000,,Just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:03.83,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Dorms, huh? I've always \Nwanted to stay in one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:03.31,italicstop,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, no! It's not perfect! \NCall me out on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:05.52,italicstop,Miku,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's a song about a one-sided crush.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:05.86,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come visit you sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:07.71,italicstop,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Blessings to all high school girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:06.95,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:08.42,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:08.77,italicstop,Miku,0000,0000,0000,,Blessings to all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.69,italics,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please listen to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:14.10,italics,Mika/Miku,0000,0000,0000,,Fukumoto Miki's "Delusion."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:18.64,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Akebi-san, you said you \Nliked this singer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.64,0:11:22.58,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Miki-chan looks super \Ncute singing this song!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:24.48,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:26.02,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:29.62,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, like what she does in this part here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.43,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the thing with the lip balm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:34.16,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You know about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:37.45,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,I don't. What does she do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:41.22,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi-chan, show her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:44.48,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't get it across \Nvery well, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:46.72,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, you can totally do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:48.44,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I even have lip balm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:53.25,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:57.40,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't even express what you \Nlove most about your favorite...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:12:00.48,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really call yourself a fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.65,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.53,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:17.05,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,But if I'm going to do it, \NI have to do it right,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:19.51,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,or it'd be an insult to Miki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:22.53,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wipe this off before I return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:23.42,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:27.59,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,She puts lip balm on two fingers like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:29.93,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,brings them up to her lips, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:13:00.49,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi-chan, do the thing where \Nyou look upward at us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:01.98,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:03.91,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:09.28,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi-chan! One more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:10.07,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:14.08,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi-san! You definitely \Ngot her appeal across!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:15.06,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:18.82,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Quit making her do it over and over! \NYou're putting her on the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:21.69,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, uh, I do not speak Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:24.07,top,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! I know you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:24.07,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,What is this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:27.34,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I feel full... in multiple ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:31.07,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:36.13,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:52.47,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:56.49,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What do you wanna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:05.24,flashback,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:10.62,flashback,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Komichi-chan, what do you want to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:13.90,flashback,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! I'll play by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.89,flashback,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep working while you watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:22.41,flashback,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I can skip two bars now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:28.68,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,How about...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:38.11,main,Teacher1,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is the closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:42.68,main,Teacher1,0000,0000,0000,,So, Tamura-sensei, how was your \Nfirst day as homeroom teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:44.52,main,Tamura,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:46.96,main,Tamura,0000,0000,0000,,I have lots of very unique students.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:48.90,main,Tamura,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I'm a little anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:49.20,sign_21313_231_Class_Roster,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-24.85\fax-0.26\pos(370,70)\clip(m 454 111 l 479 77 317 11 312 17 304 20 295 22 288 26 283 24 295 32)}Class Roster
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:49.32,sign_21313_231_Class_Roster,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-24.85\fax-0.31\pos(376,64)\clip(m 376 62 l 459 104 482 66 350 4 333 7 333 15 339 20 340 24 344 30 348 36 352 37 363 38 373 36 379 38 385 44 385 54)}Class Roster
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:49.45,sign_21313_231_Class_Roster,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-44.13\fax0.24\pos(414,14)\clip(m 512 62 l 489 85 426 22 436 18 440 13 441 1 449 1)}Class Roster
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:49.57,sign_21313_231_Class_Roster,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-47.29\fax0.24\pos(431,13)\c&H22433E&\clip(m 525 68 l 506 85 457 35 462 19 474 3)}Class Roster
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:54.46,top,Tamura,0000,0000,0000,,But I think it's going to be a fun class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:56.79,sign_21430_236_Akebi_Komichi,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-31.23\move(173,290,140,315)}Akebi Komichi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:08.47,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:11.48,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:12.63,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:15.78,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Yeah, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:42.79,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,She said, "See you tomorrow"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:44.14,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:50.71,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I got a little nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.94,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to say it tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:59.30,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Usagihara Touko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:01.51,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Ohkuma Minoru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:03.64,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Kamimoku Neko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:20.09,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Kizaki Erika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:24.52,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Kojou Tomono-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:26.41,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Shijou Riona-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:28.87,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumori Ai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:30.85,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Tanigawa Kei-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:33.88,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Tougeguchi Ayumi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:35.53,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Togano Mai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:37.17,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Nawashiro Yasuko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:39.34,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Minakami Riri-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:42.65,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hiraiwa Hotaru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:45.75,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hebimori Oshizu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:48.07,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Washio Hitomi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:54.19,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:59.05,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:14.45,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:19.14,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back. Your dad's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:28.78,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,He says he has to go back \Nto work tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:31.13,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:33.88,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,He asked where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:36.40,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to see you in your sailor uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:39.23,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Should I wait a bit before changing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:42.24,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's fine. His own \Nfault for falling asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:45.40,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you probably ran \Nand got all sweaty, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:47.66,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Let your uniform dry out a bit first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.97,0:17:49.71,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:51.46,sign_25648_273_Komichi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(248,225)}Komichi\NKao
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:29.86,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Dad? You should sleep in \Nthe bed, or you'll get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:32.55,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,I keep telling him that, \Nbut he won't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:35.79,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kao. You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:41.31,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.97,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Dad came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:44.65,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:50.40,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,The bath's ready, you two. Go on and get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:52.80,main,Komichi/Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:58.14,main,Komichi/Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Bathy, bathy, bathy, bathy, bathy time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:02.02,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:03.75,main,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:06.91,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hear any snoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:10.34,main,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's been so long, \NI got a little nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:13.22,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,So you faked being asleep? Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:16.17,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Komichi was dying to show \Noff her uniform to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:22.31,main,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't know what to say to a girl \Nher age that would make her happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.27,0:19:25.98,main,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,Komichi's grown up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:31.00,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Kao, one of the girls in class \Ntoday said I was funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:36.16,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,One even said I looked like an idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:38.22,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like you're enjoying yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:39.70,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:42.50,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go to that school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:44.07,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:47.08,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'll wear the same uniform as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:49.69,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... It's really embarrassing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.69,0:19:52.18,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,I'd show it off with pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:54.29,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a strong girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:57.43,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Pride, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:01.95,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Kizaki-san couldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:04.36,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Kizaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:09.35,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,My classmate. The one who said I was funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:10.39,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna meet her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.32,0:20:15.09,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you want me to invite her over?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:16.06,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:18.11,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:19.17,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:21.78,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,You think she'd come?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:25.65,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. You can tell her Kao said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:34.53,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it, Kao! You're such \Na good little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:37.35,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then... just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:41.05,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:42.62,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.57,0:20:53.42,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:56.55,main,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, same to you, Komichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:57.89,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:00.76,main,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,So... how was school?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:02.77,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I was kinda nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:04.56,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,But it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:05.57,main,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:06.26,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:11.24,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and there's a bunch of \Nstuff I want to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:32.63,main,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,Komichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:38.88,main,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,What time are you leaving \Nfor school in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:41.74,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.29,0:21:46.53,main,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'll have to be out of here by six.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:50.61,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll get changed before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.18,0:21:55.62,main,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:21:57.02,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.93,0:22:05.21,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.25,0:22:08.65,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
